# Windows 환경에서의 Kafka 실행

### **1. Zookeeper 실행**

> .\bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat .\config\zookeeper.properties

**포트 2181 확인**

![image-20220725175921342](C:\Users\pulpu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220725175921342.png)

### **2.Kafka 서버 실행**

> .\bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat .\config\server.properties

**포트 9092 확인**

![image-20220725180113043](C:\Users\pulpu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220725180113043.png)



### **3.Kafka 토픽 등록**

> .\bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --create --topic quickstart-events --partitions 1

#### ![image-20220725180357357](C:\Users\pulpu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220725180357357.png)

#### 3-1. 등록된 토픽 확인

> .\bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --list 

![image-20220725180416617](C:\Users\pulpu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220725180416617.png)



### **4.토픽 구독**

> .\bin\windows\kafka-topics.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --describe --topic quickstart-events

![image-20220725180639719](C:\Users\pulpu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220725180639719.png)



### **5.Producer 실행**

> .\bin\windows\kafka-console-producer.bat --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic quickstart-events

### **6.Consumer 실행**

> .\bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic quickstart-events --from-beginning



#### **최종**

Producer 콘솔에서 문자 전송시 Consumer  콘솔에서 받음

![image-20220725181415105](C:\Users\pulpu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220725181415105.png)



**추신1**

새로운 Consumer를 생성하여 총 2개의 Consumer 에서 Producer 내용 확인하기

> ###### **.\bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic quickstart-events --from-beginning**

